article_id:927,category_name:News,title_name:Regarding Void Battles Drop Reward Adjustments and Balance Adjustments to Certain Weapons,image_path:,message:<div><span style="color: rgb(44, 130, 201);"><strong>[Update <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1575883200"></span>]</strong></span><br>We have corrected some of the figures in the &quot;Balance Adjustments to Certain Weapons&quot; part of this notice:<br><br>[Before correction]<br>(Flame) Astral&#39;s Bane +40%<br>(Water) Astral&#39;s Bane +40%<br>(Wind) Astral&#39;s Bane +40%<br><br>[After correction]<br>(Flame) Astral&#39;s Bane +60%<br>(Water) Astral&#39;s Bane +60%<br>(Wind) Astral&#39;s Bane +60%<br><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div><div><br></div><hr><div>We will adjust the drop rewards for Void Battles, as well as make balance adjustments to certain weapons, in a data update to be applied around <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1576474200"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>■Void Battles Drop Reward Adjustments</div><div>We will increase the number of material items you can obtain as drop rewards from certain Void Battles quests.</div><div><br></div><div>The applicable quests and material items are described below.</div><div>・The Catoblepas&#39;s Hoof and Catoblepas&#39;s Stormeye material items you can get from Catoblepas Anemos Strike</div><div>・The Soul Vestiges and Eolian Soul material items you can get from Eolian Phantom Strike</div><div>・The Raging Fang and Smoldering Tail material items you can get from Smoldering Manticore Strike</div><div>・The Raging Fang and Greedy Tail material items you can get from Greedy Manticore Strike</div><div>・The Raging Fang and Raging Tail material items you can get from Raging Manticore Strike</div><div><br></div><div>■Balance Adjustments to Certain Weapons</div><div>1. The (Flame) Skill Haste +4% ability of weapons you can craft using material items obtained in Smoldering Manticore Strike will be changed to (Flame) Astral&#39;s Bane +60%.</div><div><br></div><div>Affected Weapons (Rarity/Type/Attunement)</div><div>・Searing Savagetail (4★/sword/flame)</div><div>・Flaming Savagetail (5★/sword/flame)</div><div>・Direblade Kagachi (4★/blade/flame)</div><div>・Great Direblade Kagachi (5★/blade/flame)</div><div>・Flamesin (4★/dagger/flame)</div><div>・Blazesin (5★/dagger/flame)</div><div>・Brutality Crux (4★/axe/flame)</div><div>・Atrocity Crux (5★/axe/flame)</div><div>・Cinder Beast (4★/lance/flame)</div><div>・Ashen Beast (5★/lance/flame)</div><div>・Flameburst Dreadbow (4★/bow/flame)</div><div>・Detonation Dreadbow (5★/bow/flame)</div><div>・Blazewing (4★/wand/flame)</div><div>・Hellwing (5★/wand/flame)</div><div>・Combustion Staff (4★/staff/flame)</div><div>・Fangflame Staff (5★/staff/flame)</div><div><br></div><div>2. The (Water) HP 70% = Strength +5% ability of weapons you can craft using material items obtained in Raging Manticore Strike will be changed to (Water) Astral&#39;s Bane +60%.</div><div><br></div><div>Affected Weapons (Rarity/Type/Attunement)</div><div>・Angry Aquatail (4★/sword/water)</div><div>・Raging Aquatail (5★/sword/water)</div><div>・Direblade Mizuha (4★/blade/water)</div><div>・Dark Direblade Mizuha (5★/blade/water)</div><div>・Bloodlust (4★/dagger/water)</div><div>・Gorelust (5★/dagger/water)</div><div>・Wave Crux (4★/axe/water)</div><div>・Maelstrom Crux (5★/axe/water)</div><div>・Tidal Beast (4★/lance/water)</div><div>・Vortex Beast (5★/lance/water)</div><div>・Wavedrinker Bow (4★/bow/water)</div><div>・Streamgorger Bow (5★/bow/water)</div><div>・Wavewing (4★/wand/water)</div><div>・Tsunamiwing (5★/wand/water)</div><div>・Tideway Staff (4★/staff/water)</div><div>・Riptide Staff (5★/staff/water)</div><div><br></div><div>3. The (Wind) Therion&#39;s Bane +15% ability of weapons you can craft using material items obtained in Greedy Manticore Strike will be changed to (Wind) Astral&#39;s Bane +60%.</div><div><br></div><div>Affected Weapons (Rarity/Type/Attunement)</div><div>・Slicing Stormtail (4★/sword/wind)</div><div>・Slaughtering Stormtail (5★/sword/wind)</div><div>・Direblade Hayate (4★/blade/wind)</div><div>・Swift Direblade Hayate (5★/blade/wind)</div><div>・Whisperfang (4★/dagger/wind)</div><div>・Mutterfang (5★/dagger/wind)</div><div>・Gale Crux (4★/axe/wind)</div><div>・Squall Crux (5★/axe/wind)</div><div>・Floating Beast (4★/lance/wind)</div><div>・Flying Beast (5★/lance/wind)</div><div>・Ill-Wind Whipper (4★/bow/wind)</div><div>・Deathwind Caller (5★/bow/wind)</div><div>・Gustwing (4★/wand/wind)</div><div>・Tempestwing (5★/wand/wind)</div><div>・Gust Staff (4★/staff/wind)</div><div>・Whirlwind Staff (5★/staff/wind)</div><div><br></div><div>4. The (Flame) High Midgardsormr&#39;s Bane +20% ability of weapons you can craft using material items obtained in Void Zephyr Strike will be changed to (Flame) High Midgardsormr&#39;s Bane +30%.</div><div><br></div><div>Affected Weapons (Rarity/Type/Attunement)</div><div>・Flame Apogee (4★/sword/flame)</div><div>・Inferno Apogee (5★/sword/flame)</div><div>・Scorching Edge (4★/blade/flame)</div><div>・Skyrender (5★/blade/flame)</div><div>・Scarlet Pain (4★/dagger/flame)</div><div>・Vermillion Pain (5★/dagger/flame)</div><div>・Heavenfire Gaze (4★/axe/flame)</div><div>・Heavenwrath Gaze (5★/axe/flame)</div><div>・Ragefire Lance (4★/lance/flame)</div><div>・Flamedance Lance (5★/lance/flame)</div><div>・Vulcan (4★/bow/flame)</div><div>・Vulcanrage (5★/bow/flame)</div><div>・Bewitching Scepter (4★/wand/flame)</div><div>・Scepter of Infinite Fire (5★/wand/flame)</div><div><br></div><div>5. The (Flame) Skill Haste +4% ability of staff weapons you can craft using material items obtained in Void Zephyr Strike will be changed to (Flame) High Midgardsormr&#39;s Bane +30%.</div><div><br></div><div>Affected Weapons (Rarity/Type/Attunement)</div><div>・Twilight Harbinger (4★/staff/flame)</div><div>・Endless Demise (5★/staff/flame)</div><div><br></div><div>6. The (Water) High Brunhilda&#39;s Bane +20% ability of weapons you can craft using material items obtained in Void Agni Strike will be changed to (Water) High Brunhilda&#39;s Bane +30%.</div><div><br></div><div>Affected Weapons (Rarity/Type/Attunement)</div><div>・Judge of Seas (4★/sword/water)</div><div>・Judge of Oceans (5★/sword/water)</div><div>・Highwater Blade (4★/blade/water)</div><div>・Highwater Slicer (5★/blade/water)</div><div>・Frost Sting (4★/dagger/water)</div><div>・Frigid Sting (5★/dagger/water)</div><div>・Ice Crash (4★/axe/water)</div><div>・Permafrost Crash (5★/axe/water)</div><div>・Strohm (4★/lance/water)</div><div>・Strohm Mare (5★/lance/water)</div><div>・Frost Gaoler (4★/bow/water)</div><div>・Everfrost Bow (5★/bow/water)</div><div>・Shade Mirage (4★/wand/water)</div><div>・Spirit Breaker (5★/wand/water)</div><div><br></div><div>7. The (Water) Skill Haste +4% ability of staff weapons you can craft using material items obtained in Void Agni Strike will be changed to (Water) High Brunhilda&#39;s Bane +30%.</div><div><br></div><div>Affected Weapons (Rarity/Type/Attunement)</div><div>・Ocean Core (4★/staff/water)</div><div>・Endless Azure Core (5★/staff/water)</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div><div><br></div>,start_time:1575871200,update_time1575883592